The comparability analysis of PK model-predicted 25(OH)D concentrations (using the popPK model derived from Part 1) was compared to observed 25(OH)D concentrations in VDORA Part 2. The overall bias and imprecision of predicted plasma concentrations was assessed through calculation of the median percentage prediction error (MPPE) and median absolute percentage prediction error (MAPE), respectively, according to the following equations:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
